      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RAKIN' IT IN (3) jumped from a low draw and boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten 2 lengths (26.38) behind Dashing Jiffy at this track. Can measure up this time. TRACK THIRTEEN (1) broke a string of placings finishing in the money two on end before a last start eighth (23.98) at this track. Should be about the mark. MANILA PLUTO (2) makes his debut without a trial but profiles well for first outing. Expected to play a major role. MANILA JACK (7) is a newcomer from the Robert Mowat kennel. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Can run a bold race on debut.",
